Here are the steps to get the GUI running:
=========================================

1.  First time, setup the GUI configuration by following the configuration steps in the configuration file.  The configuration steps need only to be completed once.

Start the GUI:
=============

2.  MongoDB must be running to start the GUI.  Navigate to the cadmium-v2 project root directory and run the mongo batch file that you configured earlier:

        mongo.bat

3.  To start the server, open a new console and navigate to the cadmium-v2 project root directory and type the following:

        node server.js

4.  Open your preferred browser and go to:

        http://localhost:8080
